{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE BOOK OF BUJA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_1.gif?t=1728922109\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The<strong> Queen of Darrow</strong> is dead. The <strong>King</strong> is on trial for her death and has asked you,<strong> Buja</strong>, to help clear his name. Using your ability to peer into a <i>corpse's final moments</i>, you follow a trail of <strong>remains</strong> to uncover the context of her demise and, hopefully, save the <strong>King and the Kingdom</strong> from an <i>impending disaster</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Collect Various Fruits and Shoot Them as Projectiles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_2.gif?t=1728922109\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Stack</strong> various combinations of <strong>fruit</strong> on your <strong>spear</strong>. Each <strong>fruit</strong> does something different!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Translate Ancient Texts with a Seer Stone</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_4.gif?t=1728922109\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Find Hidden Meaning in People's Words</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_3.gif?t=1728922109\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reveal subt<strong>let</strong>ies with the Mind Maggot, a gri<strong>me</strong>y, yet <strong>know</strong>ledgeable l<strong>if</strong>eform that burrows deep in <strong>you</strong>r ear <strong>can</strong>al and highlights th<strong>read</strong>s of <strong>me</strong>aning in text that you read.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Uncover the Mysteries of the Dead</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_5.gif?t=1728922109\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your inherited ability to <strong>peer into the dead</strong> and solve the mystery behind the <strong>Queen's death</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Find All of Your Elephant Friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_8.gif?t=1728922109\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Electrify Water to Solve Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_9.gif?t=1728922109\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Freeze Bushes to Solve Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_7.gif?t=1728922109\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solve Dozens of Interesting Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_6.gif?t=1728922109\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/Buja_GIF_10.gif?t=1728922109\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728922109","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1728922109","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728922109","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728922